PN,31001
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,FJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams all
OL,7,Fused misleading pricing in their ads
OL,8,Ffor Black Friday deals last year, the
OL,9,Fregulator has found.
OL,11,FThe Advertising Standards Authority
OL,12,F(ASA) found two John Lewis ads for
OL,13,FMacBook and ASUS laptops in the lead-
OL,14,Fup to Black Friday in November
OL,15,Foverstated the advertised price drops.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,FThe first John Lewis ad offered a
OL,7,FMacBook Air for #699 including a #150
OL,8,Fsaving on Black Friday, but the ASA
OL,9,Ffound "insufficient" data from the
OL,10,Fretailer demonstrating the laptop's
OL,11,Festablished selling price was #849.
OL,13,FIt noted third-party price tracking
OL,14,Fwebsites suggested the product had
OL,15,Fonly been sold for #849 for one day in
OL,16,FJuly 2025.
OL,26,@qD@GOUqD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,FThe ASA said it had also not seen
OL,7,Fsufficient evidence that a claimed
OL,8,F#450 drop in price for the ASUS laptop
OL,9,Fas part of John Lewis's Black Friday
OL,10,Fevent represented a genuine saving.
OL,12,FThe regulator found two ads for
OL,13,FDebenhams ` one advertising home
OL,14,Fproducts with "44%" savings, and the
OL,15,Fother featuring various products
OL,16,Fincluding a hair styling tool with
OL,17,F"21% savings" ` were misleading, while
OL,18,Fa Boots ad for a Hugo Boss fragrance
OL,19,Fadvertised as reduced from #80 to #60
OL,20,Fhad only been sold at the higher price
OL,21,Ffor 21 days when it was first launched.
OL,26,@vD@OOUvD@SO]yD@AOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,FThe ASA said in all cases, it had not
OL,7,Fseen evidence the advertised Black
OL,8,FFriday deals claims represented a
OL,9,Fgenuine saving against the usual
OL,10,Fselling price of the product, and
OL,11,Ftherefore misled consumers.
OL,13,FThe sweep is the latest by the
OL,14,Fregulator using AI-powered monitoring,
OL,15,Fand follows rulings against hotel and
OL,16,Ftravel companies in November for
OL,17,Fmaking misleading "from" price claims.
OL,26,@yD@SOUyD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,FThe ASA also banned two ads for Very
OL,7,Ffollowing complaints from the watchdog
OL,8,FWhich? over misleading reference
OL,9,Fprices and associated savings.
OL,11,FEmily Henwood, operations manager at
OL,12,Fthe ASA, said: "People rightly expect
OL,13,Fthe deals they see around Black Friday
OL,14,Fto be genuine.
OL,16,F"These rulings send a clear message to
OL,17,Fretailers and brands that promotional
OL,18,Fevents aren't exempt from the rules.
OL,26,@tD@POUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,F"We expect advertisers to be able to
OL,7,Fdemonstrate that the discounts they
OL,8,Fpromote represent real savings so that
OL,9,Fpeople aren't misled."
OL,11,FWhich? head of consumer protection
OL,12,Fpolicy Sue Davies said: "It's
OL,13,Funacceptable that well-known
OL,14,Fbusinesses have been reeling in
OL,15,Fcustomers with misleading deals.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]tD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,F"It will be reassuring to people,
OL,7,Fespecially when so many are already
OL,8,Fstruggling with cost-of-living
OL,9,Fpressures, that the ASA is taking
OL,10,Faction. This should send a message to
OL,11,Fother businesses that dodgy pricing
OL,12,Fwill not be tolerated.
OL,14,F"That being said, we find too often
OL,15,Fthat customers are being targeted by
OL,16,F'deals' that are not what they seem.
OL,17,FIt's clear that the current system is
OL,18,Fnot fit for purpose and the Government
OL,19,Fmust tighten the law to ban deceptive
OL,20,Fpricing."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,FA Debenhams spokesman said: "We note
OL,7,Fthe ASA's ruling in relation to a
OL,8,Fsmall number of marketplace product
OL,9,Fadverts from late 2025.
OL,11,F"Debenhams operates a marketplace
OL,12,Fmodel, where third-party sellers set
OL,13,Ftheir own prices and are required to
OL,14,Fcomply with all advertising and
OL,15,Fpricing regulations.
OL,26,@nD@]OUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31009
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,F"While we do not set or control this
OL,7,Fpricing, we have taken steps to
OL,8,Freinforce our guidance and
OL,9,Frequirements for third-party sellers
OL,10,Fto ensure compliance with all
OL,11,Fadvertising and pricing regulations."
OL,13,FA John Lewis spokeswoman said: "Our
OL,14,FNever Knowingly Undersold price
OL,15,Fpromise means we lower thousands of
OL,16,Fprices each week to match competitors
OL,17,F` and this activity intensifies during
OL,18,Fthe busy Black Friday period.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@eO]uD@`OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,F"While we always strive to ensure the
OL,7,Fprice claims in our advertising are
OL,8,Faccurate and compliant, we apologise
OL,9,Ffor two errors which weren't picked up
OL,10,Fwhen we lowered our prices to match
OL,11,Fothers."
OL,13,FA Boots spokeswoman said: "We know
OL,14,Fthat our customers enjoy making
OL,15,Fgenuine savings on their shopping at
OL,16,FBoots, and last year we offered
OL,17,Fdiscounts on more than 20,000 products
OL,18,Facross the Black Friday period.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@HO]uD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1779274977
OL,3,CJohn Lewis, Boots and Debenhams Black
OL,4,CFriday deal ads 'misled shoppers'
OL,6,F"We have robust measures in place to
OL,7,Fmake sure that our promotions comply
OL,8,Fwith the relevant laws and associated
OL,9,Fguidance, and we have taken learnings
OL,10,Ffrom this individual case of human
OL,11,Ferror identified by the ASA."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]
